 mysGarageDoors - README

 Summary
 =======
 
   Description
   Interactions

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Description
 ===========

 Manage the two garage doors.

 From mySensors point of view, the board manages:

  - one 'main' global child

  - two children per door:
    > an 'actor' to send and receive commands
    > a 'cover' to send position of the door.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Interactions
 ============

 +- CHILD_MAIN (S_CUSTOM)
     |
     +- C_SET
         |
         +- V_CUSTOM with payload = '1': raz the eeprom.
         +- V_CUSTOM with payload = '2': run the learning program.
      
 +- CHILD_DOOR (S_COVER)
     |
     +- C_SET
     |   |
     |   +- V_CUSTOM with payload = '1': open/close the door.
     |
     +- C_REQ
         |
         +- V_UP / V_DOWN sent when the door is opening/closing
         +- V_VAR1 with payload = 0-100 % door opened

